---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Surf Gear Basics: What You Actually Need - Surf Deeper" description="Beginner-friendly surf gear overview: wetsuits, leashes, wax/traction, and beginner board choices.">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Surf Gear Basics: What You Actually Need</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">Clear, minimal kit that works</p>
  </header>

  <article class="technique-article">
    <section>
      <h2>Wetsuits</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Thickness guide by water temp</li>
        <li>Fit tips</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Leashes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Length and thickness by board type</li>
        <li>Regular checks for wear</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Wax & Traction</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Waxing a board properly</li>
        <li>Alternatives (traction pads, spray-on)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Boards for Beginners</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Soft-top vs. fiberglass</li>
        <li>Longboard vs. funboard</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #00ff88;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .technique-article {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .technique-article section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .technique-article h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff88;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .technique-article ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .technique-article li {
    color: #00ff88;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .technique-article li::before {
    content: "â—¦";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00cc6a;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    .technique-article {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>


